{
  "crowdfunding": {
    "title": "",
    "missionTitle": "Fulfil the dream with Jyumyou offerings!",
    "bodyHtml": "<style>\n#page-crowdfunding .support-card{max-width:100% !important;}\n</style>\n<style>\n.cf-split{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) 370px;gap:28px;align-items:start;width:100%;}\n@media(max-width:860px){.cf-split{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}\n.cf-right-sticky{position:sticky;top:80px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"support-card support-card--wide\"><div class=\"support-top-stripe\"></div><div class=\"support-inner\">\n\n<div class=\"support-header\">\n  <div class=\"support-main-title\">Crowdfunding</div>\n  <div class=\"support-sub-title\">I'd be so happy if you could support me as much as you comfortably can~</div>\n  <div class=\"support-deco-line\">♡ ♡ ♡</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"cf-split\">\n\n<!-- ===== 左カラム：タブ切り替え ===== -->\n<div>\n<style>\n.cf-inner-tabs { display:flex; gap:8px; margin-bottom:20px; }\n.cf-inner-tab {\n  flex:1; padding:10px 0; border-radius:12px;\n  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);\n  background:rgba(255,255,255,.04); color:var(--muted);\n  font-weight:700; font-size:.95em; cursor:pointer;\n  text-align:center; transition:all .2s;\n}\n.cf-inner-tab.active {\n  border-color:rgba(255,121,176,.6);\n  background:rgba(255,121,176,.12); color:var(--text);\n}\n.cf-inner-panel { display:none; }\n.cf-inner-panel.active { display:block; }\n</style>\n    <div class=\"cf-inner-tabs\">\n      <button class=\"cf-inner-tab active\" onclick=\"cfTabSwitch('mv',this)\">🎬 Anime MV</button>\n      <button class=\"cf-inner-tab\" onclick=\"cfTabSwitch('soundproof',this)\">🔊 Soundproof Room</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"cf-panel-mv\" class=\"cf-inner-panel active\">\n      <div style=\"border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:20px;background:rgba(10,10,15,.7);padding:20px 22px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Kaisei Tokumin',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:6px;\">Let's make one Anime MV every month!</div>\n            <div style=\"color:var(--muted);font-size:.9em;\">Goal: ¥100,000 per month / Deadline: May 31, 2026</div>\n          </div>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-size:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.45);background:rgba(255,121,176,.12);white-space:nowrap;\"><span style=\"width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff79b0;display:inline-block;\"></span>Ongoing</span>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"font-size:.93em;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:18px;\">When monthly revenue exceeds ¥100,000, an animated MV song cover will be produced. If it falls short, a song cover without an MV may still be created depending on circumstances. Whether it is full-length or a short will be decided on a case-by-case basis.</br>Since revenue takes time to finalize, progress updates cannot be shared during the month, and achievement/non-achievement announcements will come the following month.</p>\n                 <details class=\"goods-box\" open>\n          <summary><div class=\"goods-summary\">\n            <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:10px;font-size:1.3em;font-weight:700;background:rgba(255,121,176,.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.4);color:var(--accent);\">🎯 Crowdfunding Active!</span>\n            <div><div class=\"title\">May 2026</div><div class=\"hint\">目標 ¥100,000 / May 202631日まで</div></div>\n          </div></summary>\n          <div class=\"inner\">\n            <p>MV crowdfunding is still going in May! I want to deliver a cool and cute MV to everyone!</p>\n            <p style=\"color:var(--accent);\">🎯 クラファンOngoing - May 202631日まで</p>\n          </div>\n        </details>\n  <details class=\"goods-box\" style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">\n          <summary><div class=\"goods-summary\">\n            <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:10px;font-size:1.3em;font-weight:700;background:rgba(234,179,8,.15);border:1px solid rgba(234,179,8,.4);color:#fde68a;\">⚙️ In Production</span>\n            <div><div class=\"title\">Mar–Apr 2026</div><div class=\"hint\">Achieved → In Production</div></div>\n          </div></summary>\n          <div class=\"inner\"><p>March and April were combined as a special case — since the total exceeded ¥100,000, the MV is now in production 🎬</p></div>\n        </details>\n         <details class=\"goods-box\" style=\"margin-bottom:10px;\">\n          <summary><div class=\"goods-summary\">\n            <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:10px;font-size:1.3em;font-weight:700;background:rgba(59,130,246,.15);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,.4);color:#60a5fa;\">✅ Complete!</span>\n            <div><div class=\"title\">Feb 2026 - Kokoro Yohou</div><div class=\"hint\">Achieved → MV Released</div></div>\n          </div></summary>\n          <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div style=\"position:relative;padding-top:56.25%;margin-top:8px;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dW6JQ9IP2Ao\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:14px;\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n          </div>\n        </details>\n    <details class=\"goods-box\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n          <summary><div class=\"goods-summary\">\n            <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,121,176,.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0;\">🎬</div>\n            <div><div class=\"title\">About the MV Production</div><div class=\"hint\">Purpose / Asobu's Dream / A Request to Everyone</div></div>\n          </div></summary>\n          <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div style=\"padding:14px 16px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,121,176,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.2);margin-bottom:14px;\">\n              <p style=\"font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:8px;\">📋 How the Crowdfunding Works</p>\n              <p style=\"line-height:1.8;font-size:.9em;\">When monthly revenue exceeds ¥100,000, an animated MV song cover will be produced.</b> This involves commissioning a creator to make the animated MV. (Of course, I'll be involved in the production as much as possible!)</p>\n              <p style=\"line-height:1.8;font-size:.9em;\">The reason it's monthly is because I want to make an anime MV every month.</p>\n            </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:14px 16px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(138,215,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(138,215,255,.15);margin-bottom:14px;\">\n              <p style=\"font-weight:700;color:#8ad7ff;margin-bottom:8px;\">✨ Asobu's Dream</p>\n              <p style=\"line-height:1.8;font-size:.9em;\">My dream is to direct original MVs and original songs like VTuber <b>Houshou Marine</b>, sing with heart like singer <b>DongDang</b>, and create as many expressions as I can while I'm alive!</p>\n              <p style=\"line-height:1.8;font-size:.9em;\">I want to show everyone what's inside my head, and I believe you'll love it.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"padding:14px 16px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);margin-bottom:14px;\">\n              <p style=\"font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;\">🤝 Why I Need Everyone's Help</p>\n              <p style=\"line-height:1.8;font-size:.9em;\">Having tried animation, video, and mixing on my own, I've learned that <b>doing everything alone is extremely difficult and the quality suffers.</b> I need the help of video creators, illustrators, and animators to make it together.</p>\n              <p style=\"line-height:1.8;font-size:.9em;\">For that, I need everyone's lifespans. I humbly ask for the Jyumyou's support in taking Mitarai Asobu's activities even further!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"sp-wish\">\n              <div class=\"sp-wish__body\">\n                <img class=\"sp-wish__icon\" src=\"./mita/wink.png\" alt=\"御手洗 遊\">\n                <div class=\"sp-wish__bubble-wrap\">\n                  <div class=\"sp-wish__bubble sp-wish__bubble--long\">In other words, I'm asking you to help make my dream — my selfish wish — come true!</div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </details>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div id=\"cf-panel-soundproof\" class=\"cf-inner-panel\">\n      <div style=\"border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:20px;background:rgba(10,10,15,.7);padding:20px 22px;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n        <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n          <div>\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Kaisei Tokumin',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:6px;\">Install a Soundproof Room and Contain the Screaming!</div>\n            <div style=\"color:var(--muted);font-size:.9em;\">Goal: ¥200,000 / Deadline: None</div>\n          </div>\n          <span style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-size:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.45);background:rgba(255,121,176,.12);white-space:nowrap;\"><span style=\"width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#ff79b0;display:inline-block;\"></span>Ongoing</span>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom:16px;\">\n          <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:1.35em;font-weight:900;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">Tallying in progress...<span style=\"font-size:.6em;font-weight:400;color:var(--muted);\">collected!</span></div>\n            <div style=\"color:var(--muted);font-size:.92em;\">Supporters: <span style=\"font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;\">14</span></div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"height:16px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.10);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px;\">\n            <div style=\"height:100%;width:46.8%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.9),#ff79b0);border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,127,183,.25);\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"support-cf-box\">\n          <div class=\"support-cf-inner\">\n            <div class=\"support-cf-header\">\n              <span class=\"support-cf-badge\">For support of ¥10,000 or more</span>\n              <span class=\"support-cf-title\">You'll receive 🤍</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"support-cf-rewards\">\n              <div class=\"support-cf-reward\">\n                <div class=\"support-cf-reward-label\">Special Title</div>\n                <div class=\"support-cf-reward-value\">Exclusive Title<br><span>A badge appears on your stream comments ♡</span></div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"support-cf-reward\">\n                <div class=\"support-cf-reward-label\">Exclusive Stream</div>\n                <div class=\"support-cf-reward-value\">Exclusive Stream<br><span>Archive will be saved too!</span></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:12px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.25);background:rgba(255,121,176,.07);font-size:.83em;\">💡 The title threshold is calculated based on the amount you paid, not the amount after fees. No worries!</p>\n      <details class=\"goods-box\" style=\"margin-top:14px;\">\n          <summary><div class=\"goods-summary\">\n            <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(255,122,191,.15);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0;\">🔊</div>\n            <div><div class=\"title\">Why I Need a Soundproof Room</div><div class=\"hint\">Purpose / Current Issues / Impact on Streams</div></div>\n          </div></summary>\n          <div class=\"inner\">\n            <p>The soundproof room is purely to \"expand my streaming options.\" It's not something I absolutely need to stream, so there's no deadline. I want to take my time collecting funds!</p>\n            <div class=\"sp-wish\" style=\"margin:16px 0;\">\n              <div class=\"sp-wish__body\">\n                <img class=\"sp-wish__icon\" src=\"./mita/worry.png\" alt=\"御手洗 遊\">\n                <div class=\"sp-wish__bubble-wrap\">\n                  <div class=\"sp-wish__bubble sp-wish__bubble--long\">I'm starting to think I may have set my sights a little too high...<br>Supporting at your own pace without rushing is the best way~</div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ruleline\"></div>\n            <p><b>Purpose</b></p>\n            <ul>\n              <li>Easier to stream late at night</li>\n              <li>Easier to record and stream singing</li>\n              <li>No worries about being loud during gaming</li>\n              <li>Being considerate of neighbors</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>Viewers often comment that I'm loud (in a fun way), but honestly I really am. Even my normal speaking voice is apparently quite loud. I speak louder than average to get good mic input. Even with windows and curtains closed, my voice carries to the neighbors.</p>\n            <p>Sounds from neighboring homes — babies crying, adults laughing, TV, doors, chairs — also reach my room. I'm a bit worried about those sounds getting into my streams, and lowering mic sensitivity makes my own voice harder to hear.</p>\n            <p>I currently do evening livestreams in the 8–10 PM window, but if I get a soundproof room I'd like to stream past 10 PM as well. A survey showed that viewers' peak availability is 9–11 PM. I want to try various time slots and content types without worrying about noise or hours.</p>\n                    </div>\n        </details>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- /左カラム -->\n\n  <!-- 右カラム -->\n  <div class=\"cf-right-sticky\">\n    <div class=\"support-sec-head\" style=\"margin-top:0;\"><span class=\"support-sec-icon\">⋈</span> You'll support me......right? 🖤</div>\n    <div class=\"paypal-standalone-wrap\">\n      <div id=\"paypal-container-EYJN5WA44NU9Y\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"support-list\">\n      <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n        <div class=\"support-item\">\n          <div class=\"support-nbubble\">YT</div>\n          <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n            <div class=\"support-iname\">YouTube Super Chat / Member Gifting</div>\n            <div class=\"support-inote\">Fee ~30%</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@MitaraiAsobu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">➡</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n        <div class=\"support-item\">\n          <div class=\"support-nbubble\">PP</div>\n          <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n            <div class=\"support-iname\">PayPal</div>\n            <div class=\"support-inote\">Fee 0%</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n        <div class=\"support-item\">\n          <div class=\"support-nbubble\">BO</div>\n          <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n            <div class=\"support-iname\">Tip on Goods</div>\n            <div class=\"support-inote\">Add extra when purchasing on BOOTH via \"BOOST\"<br>Fee 10%</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"https://mitaraiasobu.booth.pm/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">➡</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n        <div class=\"support-item\">\n          <div class=\"support-nbubble\">AM</div>\n          <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n            <div class=\"support-iname\">Amazon Gift Card</div>\n            <div class=\"support-inote\">Send to mitaraiasobu@gmail.com or DM the gift card number on X. Amazon.co.jp only.<br>Fee 0%</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B0F47Z7VMX\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">➡</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"support-item-row\">\n        <div class=\"support-item\">\n          <div class=\"support-nbubble\">TW</div>\n          <div class=\"support-ibody\">\n            <div class=\"support-iname\">Twitch</div>\n            <div class=\"support-inote\">送信する1ビッツにつき約1.5円受け取り<br>Fee ~30%</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <a class=\"support-item-arrow\" href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/mitaraiasobu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">➡</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:12px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,121,176,.25);background:rgba(255,121,176,.07);font-size:.82em;line-height:1.65;\">💡 <b>Important Note</b><br>YouTube and Twitch app versions may have fees exceeding 50%. We recommend supporting via the web version!</p>\n  </div>\n  <!-- /右カラム -->\n\n</div><!-- /cf-split -->\n\n<div class=\"support-footer\"><div class=\"support-footer-hearts\">♡ ♡ ♡</div><div class=\"support-footer-name\">御手洗 遊</div><div class=\"support-footer-roman\">Mitarai Asobu</div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n"
  }
}